{
  "brewsignal_version": "2.0",
  "based_on": { "standard": "BeerJSON", "version": "1.0" },
  "_comment": "Worked example for BrewSignal Recipe Format v2 (bead tilt_ui-cnzl). The `recipe` object is pure BeerJSON 1.0 (unit objects, BeerJSON field shapes) — strip the root `brewsignal` block and any BeerJSON tool reads it. The `brewsignal` block carries everything v1 buried in free-text `notes`: 79C whirlpool, warm biotransformation dry hop, water build, LODO. Per-hop extras live in brewsignal.hop_additions, aligned to ingredients.hop_additions by index (name+use echoed for humans).",

  "recipe": {
